summary: This document is an email from an unidentified sender to an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York, inquiring about access to an expired NBC News interview link regarding a British teen model lured into Jeffrey Epstein's web. It appears to be a request for information related to the Epstein case.

persons.name: Assistant United States Attorney
persons.context: The recipient of an email inquiry about accessing an NBC News interview related to the Epstein case.

keyFacts: An email was sent on October 13, 2021, inquiring about access to an NBC News interview regarding a British teen model lured into Jeffrey Epstein's web.
The recipient was an Assistant United States Attorney at the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York.
The original NBC News interview link had expired, prompting the request for access or information on how to obtain it.
